text: Rareş Orzaţa (born 16 February 1977) is a Romanian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Brașov
